Package: trajSurvR
Type: Package
Title: Longitudinal Trajectory and Survival Analysis for Proteomic Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ran", "User", email = "ran@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Wraps longitudinal proteomic workflows from the project's raw R Markdown
    analyses into reusable functions for quality control, differential analysis,
    correlation study, trajectory modeling, time-to-event analysis, event
    prediction, onset-time regression, and feature selection.
